dc_description_s: This data layer represents roads for Oneida County, Wisconsin in 2019.[The roads feature class contains information regarding centerlines of public and private roads in the county. The roads contain geocoding information as well as the road name. Some road centerlines have been GPS'd to insure their accuracy while others were digitized from aerial photography. State and Federal highways are included in this dataset, while some counties choose to digitize or represent divided highways this is not the case in this dataset.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: http://oneida.ncwrpc.info/
